**who —** KIZNAIVER — an entertainment sphere — an anime-world

**what —** Seven mismatched teenagers are forcibly bound by an experiment: hurt one, and the rest feel the pain. Pushed into closeness by a system that believes shared suffering breeds empathy, they must learn whether connection can be engineered — or only earned. Trigger's quieter, melancholy ensemble drama, scripted by Mari Okada.

